<text top="458" left="310" width="274" height="12" font="7">BETWEEN PARALLEL FLANGED BEAMS </text>
<text top="556" left="516" width="108" height="17" font="8"><b>LEGENDS :- </b></text>
<text top="601" left="518" width="183" height="9" font="2">fy = SHEAR STRENGTH OF STEEL. </text>
<text top="614" left="518" width="187" height="9" font="2">t = THICKNESS OF CLEAT ANGLE. </text>
<text top="628" left="517" width="108" height="9" font="2">dW = BEAM DEPTH. </text>
<text top="642" left="518" width="174" height="9" font="2">tw = WEB THICKNESS OF BEAM. </text>
